'''Mord''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Ciaran Bermingham]] and debuts in &quot;[[The Wolf and the Lion]].&quot; Mord is the turnkey at [[the Eyrie]]. [[Tyrion Lannister]] has to negotiate with him after being thrown into the Sky Cells.
